{"tid":1788678,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"支持「和理非」多成立工會 - 侯鎮安","createTime":"2019-12-19T01:03:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-20T06:05:42.000Z","uid":321709,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"239b1b83f1c3e5ff7b41caa7aabb5829ebcfe27a","tid":1788678,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:03:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069343&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6oBs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=6c1eb770\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069343&h=d68017ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069343</a><br />\n<br />\n「支持「和理非」多成立工會（職工會），因為「立法會功能界別選舉」，選特首的「選舉委員會選舉」，「勞工顧問委員會選舉」等，都是以「一工會一票」進行，十人的工會是一票，十萬人的工會也是一票；「和理非」成立一個工會就有一票，成立一千個工會，就有一千票，何樂而不為？只怕政府會千方百計，盡快堵塞這漏洞！<br />\n<br />\n支持「和理非」多成立工會，因為「進入體制」是「改變體制」的有效途徑，而「成立工會」則是「進入體制」的捷徑！理應趁著這個捷徑尚未被堵塞之前，多加利用！<br />\n<br />\n怎樣成立一個工會？請直接登入「勞工處」轄下的「職工會登記局」網頁，查看「籌組職工會」和《職工會條例》兩個欄目，便可深入瞭解。但針對「和理非」成立工會的特定目標，筆者也想跟大家分享一些個人看法，如下：」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069343\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069343&d=CSzjam5d59%2B0TSQi2Kgm6oBs3SnDZqPj3JJ4J4HclPc%3D&h=6c1eb770\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1069343&h=d68017ea\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1069343</a>"},{"pid":"0b297cce9c1ce3f37d6967d56c83c004db4d8ee5","tid":1788678,"uid":311583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-19T01:05:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CgxvfDH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCgxvfDH.jpg&h=8ac82a2a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jZLHRcb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjZLHRcb.gif&h=42707f7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"ht